    <note>Song(2) Lin(2) [28561] According to MS, 137.3952, Lin(2) died in Dezheng zhong at an age over 80, which would place death in the early 16th century. Lin is not listed as a grandson of Chonglu [28544], father of Na [28560], but Fuzu [28562], Na's #2 son is listed. Lin(2), of course, may have changed his mingzi, but that does not account for the chronological inconsistencies. A CHECK of Na's funerary inscription may throw some light on the problem.</note>
